{"tid":35121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"90%講普通話青少年在澳曾受種族歧視，廣東話則有八成","createTime":"2016-12-12T01:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T19:13:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d27c1cbec0ef41f837d325102c79da7ba3225e7f","tid":35121,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:13:08.000Z","msg":"受訪的普通話背景學童有九成曾受歧視，廣東話背景學童中有八成。<br />\n<br />\n調查機構Mission Australia行政總裁Catherine Yeomans對調查結果表示驚訝，認為這是一個警號。<br />\n<br />\n調查訪問2.2萬個年齡在15歲至19歲的年輕人，噹中4000人在家中說英語以外的語言，包括華語丶越南語和阿拉伯語。<br />\n<br />\n各大族群之中，以普通話受訪者受歧視的比率最高，九成受訪者稱曾受過歧視。<br />\n<br />\n這個比例在廣東話和菲律賓背景學童中佔大約八成。<br />\n<br />\n原住民及托勒斯海峽島民受歧視的比例，是非原住民的差不多兩倍。"},{"pid":"265f3cff97d8d3b7a98da16c7607a3776abf0e94","tid":35121,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"五十步笑百步"},{"pid":"3ee8f27c4d686bb7810a926232fc21eb00fcb506","tid":35121,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:21:37.000Z","msg":"班澳洲佬識鬼分咩，好明顯係班普通話玻璃心！"},{"pid":"c52392f1c252877fa5cc17aa2ed0d6ca226cc0f3","tid":35121,"uid":5751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:58:41.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得d人根本濫用'歧視'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係外國人 人地搵你黎開玩笑就預左架啦<br />\n你自己係香港都笑鳩印度人食咖哩，叫黑人做黑鬼<br />\n係外國比人開玩笑有幾岀奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474d7b70d59dc9474e270ff24e6744530ea84704","tid":35121,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得d人根本濫用'歧視'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla